title: Scrollbars should be disabled in ImageAnalyzer example
description: The scrollbars in the ImageAnalyzer example are not disabled when they should be.
OB: The scrollbars in the ImageAnalyzer example are enabled and allow for scrolling of the image.
EB: The scrollbars in the ImageAnalyzer example should be disabled and not allow for scrolling of the image.
SR: Disable the scrollbars in the ImageAnalyzer example to prevent scrolling of the image.
